{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require companies to provide free paper copies of accessible bills",
        "additional_details": "I want a law passed to prevent companies from ever charging for a paper copy of an accessible/large print bill \r\n\r\nThese must be FREE OF CHARGE to ensure Disability equality. Even disabled people\u2019s business bills!\r\n\r\nJust because we choose to work, doesn\u2019t mean our sight magically gets better as soon as we go to work!",
        "background": "At the moment, utility and large companies can charge disabled people for an accessible paper copy of their bills (e.g. large print, contrast etc)\r\n\r\nIf you\u2019re disabled and run a business, companies can charge you \u00a38 a month extra just to get an accessible paper bill!",
